sql_query.sql: SELECT "accounts"."id", "accounts"."username" FROM "accounts" INNER JOIN "follows" ON "accounts"."id" = "follows"."account_id" WHERE "follows"."target_account_id" = $1 AND "accounts"."domain" IS NULL ORDER BY "accounts"."id" ASC LIMIT $2
